lockquote><blockquote><blockquote>7月份去西藏，大約7月10-11號出發，預計可以14-20日<br />\n暫時有2個人，歡迎加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩隨時可以問/留言，希望搵到旅伴啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n資料都可以再傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n留埋tg:nathantse</blockquote><br />\n大概時間去加一</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有興趣就一齊傾下啦!<br />\n可以加我傾</blockquote><br />\n我差一個人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁就無辦法，我兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以遲幾日出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以呀，不如加我再傾"},{"pid":"2f27e8e8d6e36800e8ea7a617bafbbfe3f5fd782","tid":219770,"uid":56988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T04:36:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想就做啦！"},{"pid":"1ccdfd6a5ff5b1f6361597dd32732f47f16dd6ed","tid":219770,"uid":56988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T16:29:06.000Z","msg":"徵人:<br />\n7月中拼車走阿里大北缐，18天<br />\n<br />\n大家好！我們將會在今年 11/7- 13/7日出發到拉薩，想找人拼一團西藏阿里大北線(香港人團)。<br />\n<br />\n1. 人數：尚欠4-5人，預計包兩架車(我們已有3人)<br />\n<br />\n2. 費用預算:預計每人包車費用約&yen;8000-9000(連同三天拉薩住宿，邊防証手續)<br />\n(未包入場券，其餘住宿，飲食，到香港與拉薩的來回交通)<br />\n<br />\n4.行程：<br />\nDay 1到拉薩<br />\nDay 2 拉薩市內<br />\nDay 3 拉薩市內<br />\nDay 4 拉薩-澤當（雍布拉康、桑耶寺）<br />\nDay 5 澤當-浪卡子（羊湖）<br />\nDay 6 浪卡子-普莫雍措<br />\nDay 7 普莫雍措-日喀則<br />\nDay 8 日喀則-薩迦（布夏巴瑪峰、佩枯措）<br />\nDay 9 薩迦-馬旁雍措<br />\nDay 10 馬旁雍措-扎達（鬼湖拉昂措）<br />\nDay 11 扎達住一天（土林、古格遺跡）<br />\nDay 12 扎達-崗仁波齊<br />\nDay 13崗仁波齊-仁多（無人區、野毛牛）<br />\nDay 14 仁多-措勤（鹽湖）<br />\nDay 15 措勤-文布南村（當若雍措）<br />\nDay 16 文布南村-班戈-尼瑪<br />\nDay 17 尼瑪-納木措<br />\nDay 18 納木措-拉薩<br />\n<br />\n(基本上，Day 13-16是在無人區橫行。)<br />\n<br />\n歡迎有興趣的朋友加入, 有任何疑問也可提出一起討論呀！<br />\n<br />\n呢個行程同當地既人研究過，90後。睇下有無興趣JOIN埋一齊<br />\ntg:nathantse<br />\n<br />\n日期差少少可以再傾"},{"pid":"62d4af092cdcb1a4fdccaa9a963ef26de737c01b","tid":219770,"uid":56988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:24:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b435d34c57e0bbc5dba28e940ced6a9fcf972205","tid":219770,"uid":56988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:51:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2505ddd16a10bb8ba5870d688ae1269ff7c5a9be","tid":219770,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T07:34:25.000Z","msg":"崗仁波齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb4ce15328f29d93ca4b27e73972a1e5ba5a7f7b","tid":219770,"uid":56988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T08:36:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>崗仁波齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其中一個好想到既地方，又未算好商業既時候 盡早去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b069a3035e20a7ce8d9e65c43eafcfbe26d48117","tid":219770,"uid":56988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T15:59:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a5bf5a6c2ae9a779811a7d51c1f4f04ec2cfdb","tid":219770,"uid":56988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T16:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817d9f01221aa6f5adcc283b9ee7751b834be3ef","tid":219770,"uid":56988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57fd4eca15ccc030923a2c2447181000049b9511","tid":2197